item.title: About
item.author: vincentarchambault@icloud.com (Vincent Archambault)
item.description: Vincent Archambault I live in Montreal and I am a PhD student in computer science at the University of Montreal. I previously worked for the French bank Société Générale and lived in France for 7 years. I like to be active, travel, meditate and spend time with my family and friends. I practice among other things running, taekwondo and cross-country skiing.
